Beginner&#8217;s guide to workplace automation </h3>
<div class="entry">
<p>Losing control of your purchasing paperwork can stifle business growth. Do yourself &#8211; and your business &#8211; a favour and make the paper work for you.</p>
</div>
<div class="image-link">
<img src="https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Bureaucracy-must-die.png" width="320" height="160" class="attachment- size- wp-post-image" alt full srcset="https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Bureaucracy-must-die.png 320w, https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Bureaucracy-must-die-300x150.png 300w, https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Bureaucracy-must-die-130x65.png 130w" sizes="(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px"><noscript><img width="320" height="160" src="https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Bureaucracy-must-die.png" class="attachment- size- wp-post-image" alt="" full="" srcset="https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Bureaucracy-must-die.png 320w, https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Bureaucracy-must-die-300x150.png 300w, https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/Bureaucracy-must-die-130x65.png 130w" sizes="(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px" /></noscript> </div>
<a href="https://turbinehq.com/workplace-automation-placeholder/" class="button more-button">Free ebook</a>
</div>
<div class="feature time-off">
<h3 class="time-off">
Time off requests </h3>
<div class="entry">
<p>Track and manage staff holidays, sick days and other time off. No more untidy paperwork or missing forms. Employees can request time off quickly online. Managers can approve or reject just as easily.</p>
</div>
<div class="image-link">
<img src="https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/plugins/lazy-load/images/1x1.trans.gif" data-lazy-src="https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/holidays-mini.jpg" width="320" height="160" class="attachment- size- wp-post-image" alt="screenshot of Turbine employee calendar" full srcset="https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/holidays-mini.jpg 320w, https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/holidays-mini-300x150.jpg 300w, https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/holidays-mini-130x65.jpg 130w" sizes="(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px"><noscript><img width="320" height="160" src="https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/holidays-mini.jpg" class="attachment- size- wp-post-image" alt="screenshot of Turbine employee calendar" full="" srcset="https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/holidays-mini.jpg 320w, https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/holidays-mini-300x150.jpg 300w, https://turbine-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/holidays-mini-130x65.jpg 130w" sizes="(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px" /></noscript> </div>
